description: Try our easy to follow High Protein Cacao Mousse recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Mousse,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Quick & easy dessert,Halal,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Peanut free
name: High Protein Cacao Mousse Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add cottage cheese, unsweetened cacao powder, lemon juice & coconut sugar to your food processor.
Pulse until mixture is smooth & light.
Once smooth and light add the mousse into a small bowl & top with banana, toasted coconut & cacao nibs
